    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tFor Snow Queens Who Have Considered Suicide ...\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy Darryl Pinckney\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u201cIs your friend as pretty as you are? he asks. She\u2019s a white girl, she answers. He tells her all white women look the same.\u201d\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIn the Current Issue, Issue 240\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tLetters & Essays\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
      "url": "/letters-essays/7905/for-snow-queens-who-have-considered-suicide-because-paul-newman-in-the-first-twenty-minutes-of-paris-blues-is-too-much-darryl-pinckney"
    },
    {
      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tDonate to The Paris Review\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy The Paris Review\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe Paris Review promotes the most exciting writers of the day and supports inquisitive readers the world over.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tDonate\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
