      "text": "\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\tThe New York Review of Books and The Paris Review: Announcing Our Summer Subscription Deal\n\t\t\t\t\t\tBy The Paris Review\n\t\t\t\t\t\tJuly 1, 2022\u00a0\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tLove to read but hate to choose? Through the end of August, you really can have it all when you subscribe to both The Paris Review and The New York ...\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tThe Daily\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tBulletin\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t",
